{"tid":1699960,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過兩個人一齊去旅行最後變成各自各自由行","createTime":"2019-11-08T09:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T03:41:34.000Z","uid":193220,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d79ea9d61f4ac0420cc451e9c43f330d3502944","tid":1699960,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"去親機動遊戲樂園<br />\n博物館參觀<br />\n水族館<br />\n<br />\n每一次遊覽景點<br />\n個位朋友總係話<br />\n夾定時間到時集合<br />\n<br />\n一齊去旅行慢慢變成各自各自由行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係應該齊上齊落咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係有時候係好事<br />\n起碼唔會引起各種爭拗<br />\n大家好黎好去<br />\n返到香港起碼好相見<br />\n<br />\n不過一開始就唔應該一齊去囉<br />\n倒不如自己一條友自由行仲好<br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1b667779a18f8e3c108292c407b9b88ea19e30","tid":1699960,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a58f2f6e686a82c7b2deea6b24a0e5425ab2a88","tid":1699960,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7058b28eb62c4b7d3a624afe071525e05e0bcdbc","tid":1699960,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c495ed2c3e1b6df0834b8ea6db2617d60f56f75","tid":1699960,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:23:38.000Z","msg":"你就好"},{"pid":"811257be5a860f9618fa371a226b94130cd636d6","tid":1699960,"uid":82082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:21:53.000Z","msg":"睇你旅行為左乜？<br />\n唔鬧交各有各行無乜問題，一齊去係叫有個照應者"},{"pid":"da93a2b0939828469daac4722562b960cc68f3ff","tid":1699960,"uid":175420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20